    /// Stable, per-variant byte discriminator that paired with the
    /// recursive payload hash builds the substrate's [`Hash for Atom`]
    /// projection — `0u8` for [`Self::Symbol`], `1u8` for
    /// [`Self::Keyword`], `2u8` for [`Self::Str`], `3u8` for
