    /// closed-set [`Atom`] algebra), [`Atom::BOOL_LITERALS`]
    /// (`[&'static str; 2]` on the Scheme-bool spelling axis), and
    /// [`crate::error::UnquoteForm::MARKERS`] / [`crate::error::UnquoteForm::IAC_FORGE_TAGS`]
