    /// ONE typed method on each algebra, symmetric with the existing
    /// (Sexp value → AtomKind via
    /// `Sexp::as_atom().map(Atom::kind)`) atomic-axis composition and
    /// the direct (Sexp value → QuoteForm) marker projection
