    /// lead byte (a `~` reverse-unquote, a `?` conditional-unquote, a
    /// `#` reader-macro-lead) extends [`Self::ALL`] AND
    /// [`Self::PREFIXES`] AND [`Self::LEADS`] AND [`Self::lead_char`]'s
